dc_title_s: Parks and Recreation Facility: Boomington, Indiana
dc_description_s: Bloomington Parks and Recreation Facility areas exported from the CIty's GIS. See summary description (txt) file for information about intended use, projection, currency, attributes, etc.This map data layer represents the parks and recreations facility areas owned or maintained by the City of Bloomington, Indiana. It contains features such as city community parks, nature preserves, recreational sports facilities, recreation centers, cemeteries, pools, and more.
